    <div class="cfp whiteboard col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-12">
      <h3>Selected speakers</h3><p>To be announced in a few days. Stay tuned!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="translation whiteboard col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
      <h3>Simultaneous translation</h3><p>(en&ndash;pt / pt&ndash;en).</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="activities" class="activities">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-12">
      <h2 class="activities-work">Workshops</h2>
      <h3>Quinta (24 de Abril &mdash; Recife)</h3>
      <p>There were so many proposals that a one–day conference wasn't enough. <strong>Workshops</strong>, then! The full line-up and infos will be announced very soon. :-)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="remarks col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-12">
      <h4 class="sr-only">Observações</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Workshops are not included in the conference tickets.</li>
        <li>Passes will be sold separately.</li>
        <li>All workshops will be presented in english</li>
        <li>Limited availability.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-12">
      <hr>
      <h2 class="activities-fun">Activities</h2>
      <p>AP.Rb is also about fun. There will be activities before and after the conference. A nice time in a nice beach.</p>
    </div>
